}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Cool Hover Cards</title>
<style>

    .card {
        background: #1e2a38;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
        padding: 20px;
    }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent);
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
</style>

<div class="container">
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Card One</h3>
        <p>This is a cool hover card. It lifts and glows when hovered.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Card Two</h3>
        <p>Use it for services, features, or even portfolio items.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Card Three</h3>
        <p>Everything is fully responsive and cleanly designed.</p>
    </div>
</div>

</html>
